cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SI, cs.COMM, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper deals with the outage probability of a dual-hop relay system, which is a common topic in information theory. 
2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses a relay system with multiple antennas, which is a common topic in networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SI (Signal Processing) - The paper proposes three heuristic relay precoding schemes to combat co-channel interference, which is a signal processing problem. 
4. cs.COMM (Communication and Networking) - The paper deals with a communication system with a relay, which is a common topic in communication and networking. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses the performance of different relay precoding schemes, which can be applied to improve the quality of multimedia transmission.
